{
  "title": "Crisp Charred Venezuelan Pork Skewers",
  "description": "A spicy and tender post-workout dish featuring pork, robata-grill, and lacto-vegetarian friendly ingredients, originating from Venezuela.",
  "cuisine": "Venezuelan",
